content: Thank you for creating such a smooth game!

HOW DO YOU GET THE GREEN COMIC BOOK. I'VE BEEN STUCK FOR 3 DAYS Trying to find it. Please help, but overall a great game.
Great game, although stuck near the end. I can't seem to use the baseball bat to get into Romero's locker. Am i missing something?

Finally the highly anticipated second part is here! LOVE the new characters (specially the Capi Wachimolete) and is always great to have the old bunch of kickasses back! Double of fun, and very much longer than the first adventure! Buy it now yippee ki yay!
